        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Stop Russian Government and Oligarchs from Limiting Democracy Act of 2022 or the Stop Russian GOLD Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits a U.S. person from engaging in a transaction with a foreign person who purchases, transacts in, or transports Russian gold. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
